name: Tactical Gear - by EDG & Parrley
description:
If you'd like to support me and do more:
https://ko-fi.com/edgonkofi - commissions open!
If you're looking for a >>LoRA Making Tutorial<<

Tactical Gear - by EDG & Parrley

Hello model makers and lovers,

I am back with @ParrleyQ to get you another model that we hope you will like!

He could not manage to make his own model for the moment because kohya won't work properly for him! I would like you to please cheer him on until we find a solution!

Since I don't want him to not experience the joy of making models, he has become my assistant and he helped me into making this model. Parrley's prompting is very good and he has made preview images for the model, I hope you'll like them!

Parrley and I wish you to have fun with this LoHa and hope you see you get crazy with the reviews!

Advice for users:

This LoHa can be used at full power (weight1) safely according to our experimentations.

Be that as it may, we recognize that every user, model, and machine is different, therefore we would like you to use our prompts as base and experiment towards your preferred result.

Also since this is a LoHa, don't forget to install this extension: GitHub - KohakuBlueleaf/a1111-sd-webui-locon: A extension for loading LyCORIS model in sd-webui
